{
  "video_id": "wmMrZyVANUo",
  "title": "How architecture can create dignity for all | John Cary",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 15456.0,
      "text": "On a beautiful day, just a few years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15480.0,
      "end_time": 17896.0,
      "text": "my wife and I entered a hospital"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17920.0,
      "end_time": 19696.0,
      "text": "near our home in Oakland, California"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19720.0,
      "end_time": 21960.0,
      "text": "for the birth of our first daughter, Maya."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22600.0,
      "end_time": 25256.0,
      "text": "We had responsibly toured the birthing center in advance"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25280.0,
      "end_time": 28216.0,
      "text": "and yet we were somehow still startled to find ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28239.0,
      "end_time": 30960.0,
      "text": "in the place where we would experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30120.0,
      "end_time": 32640.0,
      "text": "one of the most significant moments of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33280.0,
      "end_time": 35776.0,
      "text": "We were stuck in a windowless room"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35800.0,
      "end_time": 39199.0,
      "text": "with no hint of the bright and sunny day that we had left."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40720.0,
      "end_time": 42400.0,
      "text": "Fluorescent lights buzzed overhead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44400.0,
      "end_time": 45839.0,
      "text": "the paint on the walls was beige"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47000.0,
      "end_time": 49416.0,
      "text": "and machines beeped inexplicably"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49440.0,
      "end_time": 52440.0,
      "text": "as a wall clock indicated day turning to night."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53160.0,
      "end_time": 55495.0,
      "text": "That clock was placed above a door"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55520.0,
      "end_time": 57496.0,
      "text": "in direct line of sight"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57520.0,
      "end_time": 61280.0,
      "text": "to where my wife lay as her contractions increased hour after hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62320.0,
      "end_time": 64135.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;ve never given birth --"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64160.0,
      "end_time": 65176.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65200.0,
      "end_time": 70960.0,
      "text": "but she assured me that the last thing that a birthing woman would ever want"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70120.0,
      "end_time": 72896.0,
      "text": "is to watch the seconds tick by."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72920.0,
      "end_time": 74760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75600.0,
      "end_time": 78950.0,
      "text": "An architect by training, I&#39;ve always been fascinated"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78120.0,
      "end_time": 81136.0,
      "text": "watching people experience design in the world around them."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81160.0,
      "end_time": 83655.0,
      "text": "I believe design functions like the soundtrack"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83680.0,
      "end_time": 85840.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re not even fully aware is playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 90150.0,
      "text": "It sends us subconscious messages about how to feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90400.0,
      "end_time": 91400.0,
      "text": "and what to expect."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92800.0,
      "end_time": 96816.0,
      "text": "That room that we were in seemed completely misaligned"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96840.0,
      "end_time": 99776.0,
      "text": "with the moment that we were experiencing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99800.0,
      "end_time": 101696.0,
      "text": "welcoming a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101720.0,
      "end_time": 104000.0,
      "text": "our daughter, into this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104480.0,
      "end_time": 107496.0,
      "text": "At one point a nurse, without any prompt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107520.0,
      "end_time": 109176.0,
      "text": "turned to us and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109200.0,
      "end_time": 110896.0,
      "text": "\"I always think to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110920.0,
      "end_time": 112776.0,
      "text": "&#39;I wish I had become an architect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112800.0,
      "end_time": 115776.0,
      "text": "because I could have designed rooms like this better.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115800.0,
      "end_time": 117150.0,
      "text": "I said to her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117400.0,
      "end_time": 119416.0,
      "text": "\"An architect did design this room.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119440.0,
      "end_time": 122176.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122200.0,
      "end_time": 125856.0,
      "text": "Despite the immense joy of our daughter&#39;s birth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125880.0,
      "end_time": 132000.0,
      "text": "the messages of that hospital room stick with she and I to this day."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133520.0,
      "end_time": 134816.0,
      "text": "Those messages are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134840.0,
      "end_time": 136336.0,
      "text": "\"You are not at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136360.0,
      "end_time": 138176.0,
      "text": "you are in a foreign place.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138200.0,
      "end_time": 140150.0,
      "text": "\"You are not in control of anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140390.0,
      "end_time": 141280.0,
      "text": "Not even the lighting.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142360.0,
      "end_time": 145640.0,
      "text": "\"Your comfort, simply, is secondary.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 147720.0,
      "end_time": 148936.0,
      "text": "At best,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148960.0,
      "end_time": 150176.0,
      "text": "a hospital room like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 152679.0,
      "text": "might just be described or dismissed as uninspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153600.0,
      "end_time": 156000.0,
      "text": "At worst, it is undignifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157200.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "And I use it to point out that none of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160400.0,
      "end_time": 161616.0,
      "text": "anywhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161640.0,
      "end_time": 164320.0,
      "text": "are immune from bad design."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 165520.0,
      "end_time": 168136.0,
      "text": "I went into architecture because I believed"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 173320.0,
      "text": "it was about creating spaces for people to live their best lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174480.0,
      "end_time": 178616.0,
      "text": "And yet what I found is a profession largely disconnected"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178640.0,
      "end_time": 182640.0,
      "text": "from the people most directly impacted by its work."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184240.0,
      "end_time": 187736.0,
      "text": "I believe this is because architecture remains"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 187760.0,
      "end_time": 191790.0,
      "text": "a white, male, elitist profession --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 191560.0,
      "end_time": 193416.0,
      "text": "seemingly unconcerned"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193440.0,
      "end_time": 196216.0,
      "text": "with some of the greatest needs in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196240.0,
      "end_time": 200520.0,
      "text": "or even the relatively simple needs of an expectant mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202400.0,
      "end_time": 204960.0,
      "text": "Students are trained in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 204120.0,
      "end_time": 206416.0,
      "text": "using highly theoretical projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206440.0,
      "end_time": 210136.0,
      "text": "rarely interacting with real people or actual communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 212976.0,
      "text": "Graduates are funneled through a long, narrow"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 215296.0,
      "text": "unforgiving path to licensure."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 215320.0,
      "end_time": 218176.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, the profession holds up a select few"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218200.0,
      "end_time": 220176.0,
      "text": "through relentless award programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220200.0,
      "end_time": 224136.0,
      "text": "focused almost exclusively on the aesthetics of buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 224160.0,
      "end_time": 227359.0,
      "text": "rather than the societal impact or contributions of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228360.0,
      "end_time": 231160.0,
      "text": "It only goes to reinforce a warped view"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231400.0,
      "end_time": 234176.0,
      "text": "of professional responsibility and success"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234200.0,
      "end_time": 237976.0,
      "text": "and yet this isn&#39;t why so many young, hopeful people"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 238000.0,
      "end_time": 239240.0,
      "text": "go into architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239720.0,
      "end_time": 241536.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not why I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241560.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "I believed then, though I didn&#39;t have a language for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 245400.0,
      "end_time": 250000.0,
      "text": "and I know now, that design has a unique ability to dignify."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 250520.0,
      "end_time": 252816.0,
      "text": "It can make people feel valued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252840.0,
      "end_time": 254960.0,
      "text": "respected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 254120.0,
      "end_time": 255760.0,
      "text": "honored and seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258360.0,
      "end_time": 262960.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;d like for you to just think about some of the spaces that you inhabit."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263520.0,
      "end_time": 267390.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to have you think about how they make you feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 268790.0,
      "end_time": 272656.0,
      "text": "Now, there are places that make us feel unhappy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 272680.0,
      "end_time": 274256.0,
      "text": "unhealthy"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 274280.0,
      "end_time": 275520.0,
      "text": "or uninspiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 279560.0,
      "text": "They may be the places that you work"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 279800.0,
      "end_time": 280280.0,
      "text": "or where you heal"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 281400.0,
      "end_time": 282280.0,
      "text": "or even where you live."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 287760.0,
      "text": "And I ask, how might these places be better designed with you in mind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 288320.0,
      "end_time": 289736.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a really simple question"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 289760.0,
      "end_time": 292599.0,
      "text": "and it can somehow, sometimes be very difficult to answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 293200.0,
      "end_time": 296296.0,
      "text": "Because we are conditioned to feel like we don&#39;t have much agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 296320.0,
      "end_time": 299416.0,
      "text": "over the spaces and places that we live, work and play."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 299440.0,
      "end_time": 301280.0,
      "text": "And in many cases we don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 301880.0,
      "end_time": 303159.0,
      "text": "But we all should."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 304400.0,
      "end_time": 307160.0,
      "text": "Now, here&#39;s a potentially dumb question for any women watching:"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 307960.0,
      "end_time": 309215.0,
      "text": "Have you ever stood"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 309240.0,
      "end_time": 311936.0,
      "text": "in a disproportionately long bathroom line?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 311960.0,
      "end_time": 313455.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313480.0,
      "end_time": 316896.0,
      "text": "Did you ever think to yourself, \"What is wrong with this picture?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 316920.0,
      "end_time": 318896.0,
      "text": "Well, what if the real question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318920.0,
      "end_time": 322376.0,
      "text": "\"What is wrong with the men that designed these bathrooms?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322400.0,
      "end_time": 328296.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 328320.0,
      "end_time": 329936.0,
      "text": "It may seem like a small thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 329960.0,
      "end_time": 332680.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s representative of a much more serious issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 333480.0,
      "end_time": 337976.0,
      "text": "The contemporary world was literally built by men"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 338000.0,
      "end_time": 341960.0,
      "text": "who have rarely taken the time to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 341120.0,
      "end_time": 343416.0,
      "text": "how people unlike them"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343440.0,
      "end_time": 345736.0,
      "text": "experience their designs."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 345760.0,
      "end_time": 348816.0,
      "text": "A long bathroom line might seem like a minor indignity."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 348840.0,
      "end_time": 350816.0,
      "text": "But the opposite can also be true."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 350840.0,
      "end_time": 354536.0,
      "text": "Thoughtful design can make people feel respected"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 354560.0,
      "end_time": 355760.0,
      "text": "and seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356400.0,
      "end_time": 359895.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve come to believe that dignity is to design"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 359920.0,
      "end_time": 362960.0,
      "text": "what justice is to law"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 362120.0,
      "end_time": 363960.0,
      "text": "and health is to medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 364840.0,
      "end_time": 366950.0,
      "text": "In the simplest of terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 366120.0,
      "end_time": 370600.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about having the spaces you inhabit reflect back your value."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372600.0,
      "end_time": 374176.0,
      "text": "Over the past two years"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 374200.0,
      "end_time": 378816.0,
      "text": "I had the opportunity to interview over 100 people from all walks of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 378840.0,
      "end_time": 381176.0,
      "text": "about their experience of design."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 381200.0,
      "end_time": 383416.0,
      "text": "I wanted to test my hunch"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 383440.0,
      "end_time": 386280.0,
      "text": "that dignity and design are uniquely related."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 387240.0,
      "end_time": 388736.0,
      "text": "I listened to Gregory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 388760.0,
      "end_time": 390976.0,
      "text": "a resident of this cottage community"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391000.0,
      "end_time": 392816.0,
      "text": "designed specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392840.0,
      "end_time": 396695.0,
      "text": "for the 50 most chronically homeless people in Dallas."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 396720.0,
      "end_time": 399456.0,
      "text": "Gregory had been living on the streets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 399480.0,
      "end_time": 403360.0,
      "text": "drifting from town to town for over 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 404000.0,
      "end_time": 405480.0,
      "text": "A broad coalition"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 406320.0,
      "end_time": 408176.0,
      "text": "of social service agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 408200.0,
      "end_time": 409616.0,
      "text": "funders and designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 409640.0,
      "end_time": 411719.0,
      "text": "created this place."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 413200.0,
      "end_time": 417336.0,
      "text": "Each 400 square foot cottage is designed beautifully"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 417360.0,
      "end_time": 418560.0,
      "text": "as a permanent home."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 419600.0,
      "end_time": 422160.0,
      "text": "Gregory now has a key"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 422400.0,
      "end_time": 423496.0,
      "text": "to a door"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 423520.0,
      "end_time": 424936.0,
      "text": "to his own house."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 424960.0,
      "end_time": 428215.0,
      "text": "He describes the sense of security that it brings him."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 428240.0,
      "end_time": 432216.0,
      "text": "Something he had lived without for three decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 432240.0,
      "end_time": 435696.0,
      "text": "When he arrived with little more than the clothes on his back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 435720.0,
      "end_time": 437176.0,
      "text": "he found everything:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 437200.0,
      "end_time": 440776.0,
      "text": "from a toaster, Crock-Pot and stove"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 440800.0,
      "end_time": 444200.0,
      "text": "to a toothbrush and toothpaste awaiting for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 445400.0,
      "end_time": 446880.0,
      "text": "He describes it simply"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 447840.0,
      "end_time": 449390.0,
      "text": "as heaven."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 450680.0,
      "end_time": 452320.0,
      "text": "On the other side of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 453360.0,
      "end_time": 455160.0,
      "text": "I listened to Antoinette,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 455400.0,
      "end_time": 457856.0,
      "text": "the director of this training and community center"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457880.0,
      "end_time": 460296.0,
      "text": "for women in rural Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460320.0,
      "end_time": 463816.0,
      "text": "Hundreds of women come to this place daily --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463840.0,
      "end_time": 465616.0,
      "text": "to learn new skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 465640.0,
      "end_time": 467150.0,
      "text": "be in community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467400.0,
      "end_time": 468896.0,
      "text": "and continue rebuilding their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 468920.0,
      "end_time": 470640.0,
      "text": "following the country&#39;s civil war."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 471200.0,
      "end_time": 474560.0,
      "text": "These women literally pressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 474800.0,
      "end_time": 477135.0,
      "text": "the 500,000 bricks"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 477160.0,
      "end_time": 481000.0,
      "text": "that make up the 17 classroom pavilions like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 481920.0,
      "end_time": 483376.0,
      "text": "Antoinette told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 483400.0,
      "end_time": 486800.0,
      "text": "\"Everyone is so proud of it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 487200.0,
      "end_time": 489376.0,
      "text": "And then back here in the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 489400.0,
      "end_time": 491560.0,
      "text": "I listened to Monika,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 491800.0,
      "end_time": 493376.0,
      "text": "the director of a free clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 493400.0,
      "end_time": 496880.0,
      "text": "primarily serving the uninsured in Arkansas."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 497720.0,
      "end_time": 501960.0,
      "text": "Monika loves telling me that the doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 501120.0,
      "end_time": 503656.0,
      "text": "who volunteer at her free clinic"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503680.0,
      "end_time": 505976.0,
      "text": "routinely tell her"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 506000.0,
      "end_time": 510280.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;ve never worked in such a beautiful, light-filled place."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 511320.0,
      "end_time": 512936.0,
      "text": "Monika believes"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 512960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515160.00000000006,
      "text": "that even people experiencing poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 515390.0,
      "end_time": 517535.0,
      "text": "deserve quality health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 517558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518855.99999999994,
      "text": "And what&#39;s more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 518880.0,
      "end_time": 522296.0,
      "text": "she believes they deserve to receive that care"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 522320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523840.00000000006,
      "text": "in a dignified setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 524640.0,
      "end_time": 528415.0,
      "text": "People like these are invaluable ambassadors for design"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 528440.0,
      "end_time": 532280.0,
      "text": "and yet they are roundly absent from architectural discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 533120.0,
      "end_time": 537256.0,
      "text": "Similarly, the people who can most benefit from good design"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 537280.0,
      "end_time": 539600.0,
      "text": "often have the least access to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 540480.0,
      "end_time": 542496.0,
      "text": "Your cousin, a homeless veteran;"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 542520.0,
      "end_time": 544960.0,
      "text": "your grandma or grandpa"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 544120.0,
      "end_time": 547616.0,
      "text": "who live in a house with a kitchen that&#39;s no longer accessible to them;"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 547640.0,
      "end_time": 549336.0,
      "text": "your wheelchair-bound sister"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 549360.0,
      "end_time": 553160.0,
      "text": "in a suburban area planned without sidewalks."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 554240.0,
      "end_time": 557816.0,
      "text": "If good design is only for a privileged few,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 557840.0,
      "end_time": 559160.0,
      "text": "what good is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 560320.0,
      "end_time": 563776.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s time designers change this"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 563800.0,
      "end_time": 566935.0,
      "text": "by dedicating their practices to the public good"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 566960.0,
      "end_time": 568696.0,
      "text": "in the model of firms"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 568720.0,
      "end_time": 570416.0,
      "text": "like Orkidstudio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 570440.0,
      "end_time": 571856.0,
      "text": "Studio Gang"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 571880.0,
      "end_time": 573736.0,
      "text": "and MASS Design Group."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 573760.0,
      "end_time": 575136.0,
      "text": "Their clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 575160.0,
      "end_time": 577736.0,
      "text": "are orphaned children in Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 577760.0,
      "end_time": 580256.0,
      "text": "foster children in Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 580280.0,
      "end_time": 582199.0,
      "text": "and pregnant women in Malawi."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 582960.0,
      "end_time": 586496.0,
      "text": "Their practices are premised on the belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 586520.0,
      "end_time": 591360.0,
      "text": "that everyone deserves good design."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 592400.0,
      "end_time": 594656.0,
      "text": "Dedicating more practices to the public good"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 594680.0,
      "end_time": 598616.0,
      "text": "will not only create more design that is dignifying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 598640.0,
      "end_time": 602160.0,
      "text": "but it will also dignify the practice of design."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 602720.0,
      "end_time": 606160.0,
      "text": "It will not only diversify the client base of design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 606400.0,
      "end_time": 610496.0,
      "text": "but it will also create new, more diverse forms of design"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 610520.0,
      "end_time": 611720.0,
      "text": "for the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 613560.0,
      "end_time": 615976.0,
      "text": "Now, in order to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 616000.0,
      "end_time": 619776.0,
      "text": "my architecture and design friends, especially my fellow white guys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 619800.0,
      "end_time": 624976.0,
      "text": "we must simultaneously and significantly diversify our ranks."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 625000.0,
      "end_time": 628216.0,
      "text": "If we want the public to believe that design is for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 628240.0,
      "end_time": 629616.0,
      "text": "and for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 629640.0,
      "end_time": 632496.0,
      "text": "Today, barely 15 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 632520.0,
      "end_time": 635175.0,
      "text": "of registered architects in the United States are women."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 635200.0,
      "end_time": 638320.0,
      "text": "And a far smaller percentage are persons of color."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 639760.0,
      "end_time": 641856.0,
      "text": "Other professions, like law and medicine"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 641880.0,
      "end_time": 645800.0,
      "text": "had made far greater strides in these crucial areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 645840.0,
      "end_time": 647896.0,
      "text": "How might our shared built environment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 647920.0,
      "end_time": 651776.0,
      "text": "our homes, our hospitals, our schools, our public spaces --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 651800.0,
      "end_time": 653550.0,
      "text": "be shaped differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 653800.0,
      "end_time": 654456.0,
      "text": "if women and people of color"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 654480.0,
      "end_time": 657136.0,
      "text": "were behind half of the proverbial blueprints?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 657160.0,
      "end_time": 659256.0,
      "text": "It is not a question of whether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 659280.0,
      "end_time": 660976.0,
      "text": "but to what extent"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 661000.0,
      "end_time": 663456.0,
      "text": "our buildings, our landscapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 663480.0,
      "end_time": 666160.0,
      "text": "our cities and our rural communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 666400.0,
      "end_time": 669175.0,
      "text": "are less beautiful, less functional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 669200.0,
      "end_time": 671856.0,
      "text": "less equitable and less dignifying"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 671880.0,
      "end_time": 676800.0,
      "text": "because women and people of color are less likely to be creating them."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 676880.0,
      "end_time": 680560.0,
      "text": "As Winston Churchill famously noted in 1943"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 680800.0,
      "end_time": 681696.0,
      "text": "when he called for the rebuilding"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 681720.0,
      "end_time": 684416.0,
      "text": "of London&#39;s war-damaged parliamentary chambers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 684440.0,
      "end_time": 689200.0,
      "text": "\"We shape our buildings, and afterward, they shape us.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 690520.0,
      "end_time": 693936.0,
      "text": "The good news is that we can change how we build"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 693960.0,
      "end_time": 695656.0,
      "text": "and who we build for."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 695680.0,
      "end_time": 698736.0,
      "text": "Be that a health worker in rural Rwanda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 698760.0,
      "end_time": 702600.0,
      "text": "or a birthing mother and nervous new father in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 703160.0,
      "end_time": 705616.0,
      "text": "We can do this by recommitting architecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 705640.0,
      "end_time": 709360.0,
      "text": "to the health, safety and welfare of the public."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 709960.0,
      "end_time": 711856.0,
      "text": "This will pay dividends."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 711880.0,
      "end_time": 714736.0,
      "text": "Because once you see what design can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 714760.0,
      "end_time": 716400.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t unsee it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 716720.0,
      "end_time": 719560.0,
      "text": "And once you experience dignity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 719800.0,
      "end_time": 721656.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t accept anything less."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 721680.0,
      "end_time": 723800.0,
      "text": "Both become part of your possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 724920.0,
      "end_time": 728656.0,
      "text": "One of my favorite conversation partners is my 90-year-old grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 728680.0,
      "end_time": 731575.0,
      "text": "Audrey Gorwitz, from Oshkosh, Wisconsin."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 731600.0,
      "end_time": 734256.0,
      "text": "After one of our conversations about design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 734280.0,
      "end_time": 735576.0,
      "text": "she wrote me a letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 735600.0,
      "end_time": 737280.0,
      "text": "She said, \"Dear Johnny,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 738360.0,
      "end_time": 741160.0,
      "text": "I thought the other day, as I sat in my doctor&#39;s office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 741400.0,
      "end_time": 742295.0,
      "text": "how depressing it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 742320.0,
      "end_time": 744936.0,
      "text": "from the color on the wall, to the carpet on the floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 744960.0,
      "end_time": 746960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 746120.0,
      "end_time": 747896.0,
      "text": "Now I will have to call to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 747920.0,
      "end_time": 750575.0,
      "text": "who is responsible for the drabness in that place.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 750600.0,
      "end_time": 752736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 752760.0,
      "end_time": 754656.0,
      "text": "In the same letter, mind you, she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 754680.0,
      "end_time": 756856.0,
      "text": "\"I did call, and I got the man in charge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 756880.0,
      "end_time": 759496.0,
      "text": "and he said he appreciated someone calling him."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 759520.0,
      "end_time": 762896.0,
      "text": "My doctor&#39;s office is now on the list for an upgrade.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 762920.0,
      "end_time": 764415.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 764440.0,
      "end_time": 765976.0,
      "text": "She signed it by saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 766000.0,
      "end_time": 768560.0,
      "text": "\"It is always good to express one&#39;s opinion"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 768800.0,
      "end_time": 769456.0,
      "text": "if done in a proper manner.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 769480.0,
      "end_time": 771736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 771760.0,
      "end_time": 775560.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 775800.0,
      "end_time": 776456.0,
      "text": "I love my grandma."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 776480.0,
      "end_time": 777976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 778000.0,
      "end_time": 779776.0,
      "text": "Like my grandma Audrey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 779800.0,
      "end_time": 783256.0,
      "text": "you deserve good design."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 783280.0,
      "end_time": 785160.0,
      "text": "Because well-designed spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 785400.0,
      "end_time": 788536.0,
      "text": "are not just a matter of taste or a questions of aesthetics."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 788560.0,
      "end_time": 792550.0,
      "text": "They literally shape our ideas about who we are in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 792800.0,
      "end_time": 793480.0,
      "text": "and what we deserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 794800.0,
      "end_time": 796496.0,
      "text": "That is the essence of dignity."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 796520.0,
      "end_time": 800616.0,
      "text": "And both the opportunity and the responsibility of design"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 800640.0,
      "end_time": 801856.0,
      "text": "for good"
    },
